data.description: Beautifully renovated 4 bed 2 bath home on a large CORNER LOT.  Upgrades include luxury vinyl "wood" floors throughout (no carpet), stainless steel appliances (not shown in photos but now installed), white wood cabinetry, solid surface countertops and vaulted ceilings.  Freshly painted, new lighting. Master bath features dual sinks, soaking tub, and glass enclosed shower.  Large back yard - plenty of room for a pool.  Fresh landscaping and mulch.
